name: Agent 386
description: Agent 386 is investigating a clue that leads him to a shady barbershop in Amsterdam. Little does he know that he is being tailed by mercenary Boris Kloris.

name: Box Assassin
description: A pizza delivery boy finds himself in the middle of a clash between a gangster boss and a legendary assassin who the boy has unknowingly delivered.

name: Object at Rest
description: The life of a stone as it travels over the course of millennia, facing nature's greatest obstacle: human civilization.

name: Turning Point
description: Animals and humans switched places. Now, animals are ruling the earth and humans are at the verge of extinction.
